# 🌟 Profile Card — HNG Frontend Task

This project is a **multi-section, responsive, and accessible Profile Card Web App** built using **semantic HTML**, **modern CSS**, and **vanilla JavaScript**.  
It’s designed as part of the **HNG Frontend Internship** and extends the core profile card with **About** and **Contact** pages for a richer experience.

---

## 🧠 Features

- ✅ Semantic, accessible HTML5 structure  
- ✅ Dynamic real-time clock using `Date.now()` (milliseconds)  
- ✅ Responsive design for mobile, tablet, and desktop  
- ✅ Avatar image with alt text and fallback  
- ✅ Social links that open in new tabs (with `rel="noopener noreferrer"`)  
- ✅ “About Me” and “Contact” pages with accessible forms  
- ✅ Form validation with error feedback and success message  
- ✅ Smooth navigation between pages (Profile / About / Contact)  
- ✅ Clean, minimal UI that adapts to screen size  

---

